<ul>
<li><strong>Hosting, Support Services.</strong> VIP Hosting/Support and VIP Support services are provided by Automattic under the terms and conditions for each such service, which are located at <a href="http://vip.wordpress.com/hosting-tos/">vip.wordpress.com/hosting-tos</a> and <a href="http://vip.wordpress.com/support-tos/">vip.wordpress.com/support-tos</a>, respectively. By signing up for a VIP Hosting/Support or VIP Support services account, you agree to abide by such terms and conditions.</li>
